issue.title: Replace webgl earth with cesium.js
issue.body:
https://cesium.com/cesiumjs/

Cesium is the core of webgl earth and has been recently updated. It’s api gives you more options as well.

issue.title: Div for Earth is Selectable on Mobile
issue.body:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/924916/is-there-a-way-to-make-a-div-unselectable

We should make the div nonselectable on mobile as to not interfere with earth movement.
